<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Bang ka bawl die Lalpa tuni'n?
 Na Chanchin Pha thu phuong dingin;
 Tuipi khela mite hilh din,
 Hinna thak Nanga kimu chuh?

[V2]
 Lalpa, tunin ei pui zelin,
 Kal khata masuon zel dingin;
 Thil tamzaw diek bawl thei dingin,
 Lalpa ei pui in ka zawh ma'n.

[V3]
 2. Lalpa, khupdin in paucham ka,
 Tuni a Na thu gente dingin;
 Gamdanga chengte a dingin,
 Thagau mangten a hun pawm na'n.

[V4]
 3. Ka thilneih ka hun piei Lalpa,
 Mite'n Na thu a het na'ng un;
 Midangte'n le Na thu ngai hen,
 Kei banga tat ahih na'ng un.

[V5]
 4. Lalpa, chieh ingting, gen ingka,
 Gitloh thima chengte kiengah;
 Krista gilote dinga thi,
 Micheng dinga khetden a um.</lyrics>
<title>LORD, LEAD ME ON</title>
<hymn_number>262</hymn_number>
<author>R.C. Paddock Tune : III Alexander 165</author>
</song>